data.name: Healthy baby snake plant pups
data.description:
It's a popular indoor plant for good reasons! Also known as Mother-In-Law's Tongue, it's one of the most efficient houseplants that purifies the air, requires minimal care, and glows with natural brightness to light up any corner of the room!

You will receive 4-5 snake plant pups (those in pot as shown): Sansevieria trifasciata species. Two consist primarily of stems, cut and propogated; leafy ones were grown from seedlings. Current height ranges from 7 to 11". Mature height can reach 2+ ft.

**Will ship all plants without pot, partially bare-root, to keep shipping costs low.

A hardy species that does best in indirect sunlight. Will package carefully and also prepare a further note on plant care instructions.

Please allow a longer pre-shipment process: 1-3 days. I will be getting your plant ready for its trip at this time!

Please let me know if you have any questions about the plant or its shipping before purchase!
